OL,3,CTrade union threatens legal action
OL,4,Cover winter fuel cut
OL,6,FA major trade union has threatened
OL,7,Flegal action over the government's
OL,8,Fdecision to means-test winter fuel
OL,9,Fpayments.
OL,11,FAround 10 million pensioners will no
OL,12,Flonger receive the benefit from this
OL,13,Fwinter after the government decided to
OL,14,Frestrict payments to people on pension
OL,15,Fcredit in a bid to save money.
OL,17,FMinisters said the move was necessary
OL,18,Fto help fill a #22 billion "black
OL,19,Fhole" they claim the previous
OL,20,Fgovernment left in this year's
OL,21,Fspending plans.
