OL,6,FBut the trade union Unite said it
OL,7,Fbelieved the cut to winter fuel
OL,8,Fpayments would have a "terrible
OL,9,Feffect" on millions of pensioners and
OL,10,Fdemanded the government reverse its
OL,11,Fdecision or face a judicial review.
OL,13,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,14,Fsaid: "People do not understand, I do
OL,15,Fnot understand how a Labour government
OL,16,Fhas taken away the fuel allowance of
OL,17,Fmillions of pensioners just as winter
OL,18,Fapproaches.
