OL,6,F"Given the failure to rectify this in
OL,7,Fthe budget, Unite has now commenced
OL,8,Fjudicial review proceedings
OL,9,Fchallenging the legality of the policy.
OL,11,F"It is not too late for Labour to
OL,12,Fregister the hurt that this cruel
OL,13,Fpolicy has caused, step back from
OL,14,Fpicking the pockets of pensioners and
OL,15,Fdo the right thing."
