OL,3,CTrade union threatens legal action
OL,4,Cover winter fuel cut
OL,6,FThe government also conducted an
OL,7,F"equalities analysis", which was
OL,8,Freleased under the Freedom of
OL,9,FInformation Act, but has been
OL,10,Fcriticised for not carrying out a full
OL,11,Fimpact assessment of the policy.
OL,13,FUnite has given the Government until 7
OL,14,FNovember to respond to a pre-action
OL,15,Fletter sent last week and reverse the
OL,16,Fcut, otherwise it would request
OL,17,Fpermission from the High Court for a
OL,18,Ffull judicial review.
