OL,6,FThe push for a judicial review of the
OL,7,Fpolicy will further strain relations
OL,8,Fbetween Labour and Unite, which had
OL,9,Fpreviously been a significant donor to
OL,10,Fthe party.
OL,12,FThe union has already expressed
OL,13,Fopposition to the winter fuel payment
OL,14,Fcut, staging a protest outside this
OL,15,Fyear's Labour Party conference over
OL,16,Fthe issue.
